                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 121rb: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 121rb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ጐልአ። ዘወሀበቶ፡ ወይዘሮ፡ ጥሩነሽ፡ አስገዶም፡ አረዛ፡ ወይኵና፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግስተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ወአቡሃ፡ አስገዶም፡ ወእማ፡ ወለተ፡ መስቀል፡ ወወለታ፡ በለጠች፡ ወይክፍሎሙ፡ አስበ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ በመስፍና፡ ሽም፡ አጋሜ፡ ካሣ፡ ወለጳጳስና፡ አቡነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡… </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of the work and the internal number of the monastic library (24-2 2418193) are written on fol. 1r.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasures: e.g., fols. 66ra, 73va, 120ra.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words written interlineally: e.g., fols. 3vb, 8vb, 18vb, 29rb, 110rb; sometimes in a secondary hand, e.g., 3ra.&#xD;
- The scribe used compressed script: e.g., fols. 30ra-31ra, 54ra-54vb, 65va-66ra.&#xD;
- Scribbles and doodles: e.g., fols. 3r, 7v, 11v, 19r, 27r, 31r.</item>
                     </list>
